microcom (2016.01.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release
    + microcom now uses autotools.  It also autodetects the presence of
      include files needed for CAN support. This allows using "any" instead of
      "linux-any" as the build-target.
    + LFS fixes
  * switch maintainer entry to debian.org address

 -- Uwe Kleine-König <ukleinek@debian.org>  Sat, 09 Jan 2016 21:52:20 +0100

